-autopackages.doc: Tells `kappak` to not automatically include packages.

-maths.theoremStyles.doc: Do not use theorem styles for theorem environments.

bbStyle.doc: Sets the mathematical blackboard letter style.

bibliographyStyle.doc: Sets the bibliography style. Only relevant if you use `kdocument` instead of the standard `document` environment.

categoryStyle.doc: Sets the category style for category theory.

headerFooterStyle.doc: Sets the header and footer style.

language.doc: Sets the language of the document.

numberTheoremsWithin.doc: What counter theorems should be numbered from.

newcategory.doc: Shorthand to define new categories. For instance : `\newcommand{\sSet}{s}{S}{et}`, or `\newcategory{\Grp}{}{G}{rp}`

op.doc: The op exponent for dual categories.
